Package gui.tools

DEAL tools: DEAL method classes (DuplicateSceneDetector, DomainModelGenerator, Extractor, Simplifier) and classes implementing the record and replay functionality.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DomainModelGenerator
    Creates a domain model based on a corresponding Scene.
    DuplicateSceneDetector
    Detects duplicate scenes in the list of stored scenes or domain models.
    Extractor
    Extracts a domain model from the given scene.
    Recorder
    Performs physical recording of commands performed on the UI into a text file located on the local disk, or into a list of UiEventSequence objects.
    RecorderRegistator
    In order for the Recorder to work, each component in the UI has to be registered with it.
    Replayer
    Not yet implemented.
    Simplifier
    Simplifies the given domain model.
